<article class='story personal-story'>
  <h1>The RavenRidge Blog</h1>
  <p>We grow hemp following regenerative practices, we make cbd products from that hemp, and in so doing, we engage more deeploy with the living world outside our doors.</p>
  <p>You'll find narrative and informational content about these topics and more in the blog posts below.</p>
  <p><em>For the full archive, <a href='#blog_archive'>skip to the end</a>.</em></p>
  {{#each content.posts_by_category}}
  <section>
    <h2>{{title}}</h2>
    <div class='flex_box post_list'>
      {{#each posts}}
        {{#if featuredImage}}
          <a href='/blog/{{slug}}'><img src='{{featuredImage}}'/>{{title}}</a>
        {{/if}}
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </section>
  {{/each}}
  <section id='blog_archive'>
    <h2>Full Blog Archive</h2>
    <ul class='padded_list no-decoration'>
    {{#each content.posts}}
      <li><a href='/blog/{{slug}}'>{{title}}</a></li>
    {{/each}}
    </ul>
  </section>
</article>

